Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>FRZ  France, EC.
    ESZ  Spain, EC.
    DEZ  Germany, EC.
    GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
    JPZ  Japan, Asia.
    USZ  United States of America.
</CN>
